            <p class="featured-post-date">&mdash; 2 October 2025</p>
            <p class="button"><a class="button-inline-outline" href="#the-blurb">[Read it]</a><span
                    class="button-tag">
                    (/blog/on-household-incomes-and-wealth)</span></p>
